author: Inside Edition
description: These people got so happy that they collapsed. In August of 2023, this father-to-be was on the floor while the mom-to-be was in labor. In August of 2025, a woman collapsed after winning a beautiful dress owned by Princess Diana at an auction for $520,000. In 2018, the excitement was too much to handle for Clara Sosa from Paraguay, and she fainted on stage after winning Miss Grand International. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: People Who Got so Happy, They Collapsed

author: Inside Edition
description: One young woman was blown away after her bedroom was packed with all her friends celebrating where she is going to college. The room was transformed with the colors of the college she is starting this fall. It's part of a trend called "bed parties." Haley's parents spent around $3000 to throw her bed party and hired an event planner. She lives in Roslyn Heights, New York, and she is headed to Florida State University.
title: What are 'Bed Parties?'
